1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:06,050
In this video, we are going to learn how to use clean architecture with domain driven design.

2
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:13,130
Clean architecture focuses on separating concerns into layers, ensuring that dependencies are directed

3
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:15,620
outwards from the core business logic.

4
00:00:16,070 --> 00:00:21,770
On the other hand, domain driven design is centered around the domain model, which represents the

5
00:00:21,770 --> 00:00:23,510
business and its rules.

6
00:00:23,510 --> 00:00:29,540
It emphasizes understanding the business domain, creating a ubiquitous language, and aligning the

7
00:00:29,540 --> 00:00:31,940
software design closely with the domain.

8
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:34,640
You can find the architecture images on the slide.

