In here we have concentric circles and each representing different layers of the application.

11
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:48,200
And also you can see clean architecture layers in rectangles with specifying the dependencies.

12
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:52,310
And here you can find the domain driven design layers and dependencies.

13
00:00:52,310 --> 00:00:54,950
And it is very similar with the clean architecture.

14
00:00:54,950 --> 00:00:58,610
And this will be an implementation of the domain driven design layers.

15
00:00:58,610 --> 00:01:04,700
If we look at the dependency of this architecture, you can see that the dependencies are explaining

